## ğŸ›£ Roadmap

The goal of `rtcomm` is to offer full SignalR-like functionality in Python â€” scalable, secure, and cross-platform. Here's what's planned:

### âœ… Initial Release
- [x] WebSocket Hub with FastAPI
- [x] JSON-based SignalR Hub Protocol
- [x] Client-to-server & server-to-client method invocation
- [x] Basic authentication via access tokens
